00:30:47.680 --> 00:30:51.599
But Andy, one of the most upvoted questions so far is,

00:30:51.599 --> 00:30:55.400
are there R packages that help with EHR data wrangling?

00:30:57.359 --> 00:30:58.800
Good question.

00:30:58.800 --> 00:31:02.160
So that is something that I skimmed over

00:31:02.160 --> 00:31:05.280
when I went through the discussion around technologies.

00:31:07.119 --> 00:31:07.959
There it is.

00:31:07.959 --> 00:31:09.359
I skimmed over that.

00:31:09.359 --> 00:31:11.119
So what we actually do,

00:31:11.160 --> 00:31:15.239
I did say that the technology provider that we use

00:31:15.239 --> 00:31:17.640
to help us do what we do is Health Catalyst.

00:31:17.640 --> 00:31:20.479
What we actually wind up doing is Health Catalyst

00:31:20.479 --> 00:31:24.119
provides a lot of R backend services in terms of ETL.

00:31:24.119 --> 00:31:26.439
And they have a set of tools that they have developed,

00:31:26.439 --> 00:31:29.040
which we use to actually help us manage

00:31:29.040 --> 00:31:30.640
all of that complexity.

00:31:30.640 --> 00:31:32.040
And so what we actually do,

00:31:32.040 --> 00:31:35.760
we describe our data warehouse as a layered cake.

00:31:35.760 --> 00:31:40.520
And that first level of, well, we technically do ELT,

00:31:40.560 --> 00:31:41.760
but we extract load

00:31:41.760 --> 00:31:44.040
and then later we do the transformations.

00:31:44.040 --> 00:31:45.719
We use the Health Catalyst tools

00:31:45.719 --> 00:31:50.000
to actually do that initial export out of the EHRs

00:31:50.000 --> 00:31:51.040
into the data warehouse.

00:31:51.040 --> 00:31:54.199
So no, we are not using any R packages for that.

00:31:54.199 --> 00:31:57.359
There are really good R packages to help you

00:31:57.359 --> 00:32:00.000
with diagnosis groupings and things like that

00:32:00.000 --> 00:32:01.160
that are useful,

00:32:01.160 --> 00:32:04.640
but they're very well made B tools

00:32:04.640 --> 00:32:06.680
but we are not using those at this point.

00:32:07.680 --> 00:32:08.680
Thank you.

