Yeah, one question that came to my mind

00:44:34.959 --> 00:44:37.560
when you were speaking about,

00:44:37.560 --> 00:44:41.639
I think it was the CCR and identifying special populations

00:44:41.639 --> 00:44:44.159
as whether or not you ever incorporate data

