their CIO and I have been having conversations about that.

00:45:09.919 --> 00:45:13.919
And somewhere here, just to see if I can find it.

00:45:15.000 --> 00:45:17.639
I actually got, I don't remember the brand

00:45:17.639 --> 00:45:19.479
that they're talking about implementing,

00:45:19.479 --> 00:45:21.120
but I actually bought some of the devices

00:45:21.120 --> 00:45:23.239
so I could start playing with the API.

00:45:23.239 --> 00:45:26.760
Because yeah, we are trying to figure out how to do that

00:45:26.760 --> 00:45:28.399
and start actually doing that.

00:45:28.399 --> 00:45:33.399
And that is something that is in the next,

00:45:33.800 --> 00:45:35.560
oh, two to five years,

00:45:35.560 --> 00:45:38.320
I think is going to be extremely exciting

00:45:38.320 --> 00:45:40.479
in this ambulatory space.

00:45:40.479 --> 00:45:42.760
I mean, everything, you know, this is a Garmin.

00:45:42.760 --> 00:45:45.120
A lot of people have Apple watches, just this.

00:45:45.120 --> 00:45:47.840
Like, the other day I was having a really,

