00:47:22.679 --> 00:47:24.239
So we are not doing that

00:47:24.239 --> 00:47:26.199
because like I was saying earlier,

00:47:26.199 --> 00:47:29.080
what we are really focused on is ambulatory care.

00:47:29.080 --> 00:47:32.439
