we are highlighting that for providers

00:48:18.840 --> 00:48:21.320
based off HIE messaging so that they know

00:48:21.320 --> 00:48:24.080
and can provide appropriate transition of care

00:48:24.080 --> 00:48:26.040
and follow-up care for those patients.

