00:52:38.040 --> 00:52:40.080
So we have a readmission risk model,

00:52:40.080 --> 00:52:43.040
and chronic diseases play a part in that model

00:52:43.040 --> 00:52:45.320
because people with lots of chronic diseases

00:52:45.320 --> 00:52:47.159
are more likely to be very obviously sick,

00:52:47.159 --> 00:52:49.080
