00:52:54.280 --> 00:52:57.679
and even more importantly, things connected to their A1c,

00:52:57.679 --> 00:52:58.959
because that would help us understand

00:52:58.959 --> 00:53:03.040
if it was a diabetes-related inpatient stay or not.

00:53:03.040 --> 00:53:05.199
So things like that would be used in a model

00:53:05.199 --> 00:53:07.399
to help predict something like a readmission risk.

00:53:07.399 --> 00:53:09.919
