And one of the, honestly, in a way,

00:59:18.800 --> 00:59:21.120
unfortunate side effects of that

00:59:21.120 --> 00:59:23.639
is I don't always know or have transparency

00:59:23.639 --> 00:59:25.159
into how providers are using it.

00:59:25.159 --> 00:59:28.280
So I don't know necessarily to look.

00:59:28.280 --> 00:59:31.320
So a doctor can get that chronic conditions report

00:59:31.320 --> 00:59:32.959
and go, oh, I got this thing,

