because in order to get that list of patients

00:59:42.320 --> 00:59:44.479
they want to go do, you know, work with,

00:59:44.479 --> 00:59:46.520
they don't have to ask me anymore.

00:59:46.520 --> 00:59:49.840
I've almost, in a way we've cut ourselves out of the loop.

00:59:49.840 --> 00:59:51.560
And so they can go do that thing

00:59:51.560 --> 00:59:52.639
and we don't even know to look.

00:59:52.639 --> 00:59:56.840
So like monitoring lab values across all lab values,

00:59:56.840 --> 00:59:59.560
across all sites, looking for signals

00:59:59.560 --> 01:00:01.560
is guaranteed to be, you know,

01:00:01.560 --> 01:00:04.560
lead you down the path of false signals.

